    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm selling my trusty car and it is honestly such a joy to drive. It's been really well-taken care of and is in great shape for its next owner. It runs smoothly, looks wonderful, and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes! I've absolutely loved having it, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
