    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The factory limited-slip differential provides excellent lock-up, and the suspension remains taut with predictable turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust and the throttle mapping remains sharp. A visceral, driver-spec example optimized for performance over show.",
