    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. It runs beautifully and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a smooth, worry-free ride that's ready to go right now, come take a look! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you might have.",
      "price": 32500.0,
