    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint retains excellent depth, while the interior shows only minor bolster wear consistent with its well-maintained history. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
